snippet.textDisplay: VIDEO SUMMARY: Maanu and Annural are two singers who have a budding romance. Their love is symbolized by a scarf Maanu gives Annural. One night, after a performance, Maanu sees Annural's assistant leaving her room, sparking jealousy and doubt. Despite these feelings, he continues to perform and later discovers the scarf in her assistant's room. Heartbroken, he leaves without explanation, boarding a train. Annural, unaware of the misunderstanding, races to the train station, only to find the scarf and miss Maanu.
